data.title: Volume 4 (In Memory of Nancy York Carroll)
data.meta_description:
Volume 4 (In Memory of Nancy York Carroll) by NOTES, released 27 July 2014

1. Dennys Dantas - Sweet Heaven
2. Polipoli8 - Far Flying Orchid
3. Robotpie - Serenade
4. Luis Cruz - Nancy
5. CyberSlunk - Eternal Star
6. Xe Cube K - T.B.G.O.S.
7. Lyric Ferchaud - Mudokon Pops
8. Pierre Vogt - The Mask
9. Bucketbot - Remembering
10. Jimmy Jammer - Planeta B e A Sua Lua Nancy
11. The Spunky - Not Again
12. Lori - Forever Here, Forever You
13. Kro - Candles
14. Clam Manson - Ocean Memory Of
15. Tear - Forever In The Stars
16. GoldWater - Oversoon
17. Deivid - The Mutant Chronicles
18. Charlie Burns - Sanguine Scriptorium
19. Space Captain - For Those Who Still Dream
20. Ollie Turbitt - Mother Hen
21. Acid Bucketbot - Never Gone
22. Fractal Shadow - Serenity Sunrise
23. Salem - Lluvia
24. Sirkostik - Lack Of Presence
25. Lotus Hands - You're Mine, Only Mine

During the preparations for "Volume 3", Fractal Shadow contacted me and shared with me the idea of ​​​​make an album in order to convey our support for Buckethead after the hard loss of his mother. The proposal traveled faster and "Volume 4" required building the first Double Volume.
Many thanks to the "Buckethead.tk" group for make this possible.

-Salem
